<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Batch {{batchNumber}} – Approval Required</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
            padding: 40px 48px;
            color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin: 8px 0 0;
        }

        /* Summary Stats Area */
        .stats-grid {
            display: flex;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .stat-item {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .stat-item:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        /* Main Content Body */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 48px;
        }

        .intro {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* Vendor Preview Table */
        .preview-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #334155;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .vendor-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .vendor-table th {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            padding: 12px 8px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .vendor-table td {
            padding: 14px 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .vendor-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .vendor-bank {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .amount-col {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #059669;
        }

        .more-indicator {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* Actions Section */
        .actions {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 16px 36px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        /* Remote Approval Note */
        .remote-note {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fef3c7;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .remote-note h4 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.025em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .remote-note p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Info Card */
        .info-panel {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .info-key {
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .info-val {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #334155;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .stats-grid { flex-direction: column; }
            .stat-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
            .content { padding: 30px 24px; }
            .header { padding: 30px 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <span class="badge">Action Required</span>
            <h1>Payment Approval</h1>
            <p>Batch {{batchNumber}} is ready for your review</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Summary Stats -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-label">Total Amount</div>
                <div class="stat-value">{{currency}} {{totalAmount}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-label">Total Items</div>
                <div class="stat-value">{{totalItems}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-label">Priority</div>
                <div class="stat-value" style="color: #ef4444;">Normal</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p class="intro">Hello {{approverName}},</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 32px; color: #475569;">A new payment batch has been compiled and submitted by <strong>{{submittedBy}}</strong>. Please review the vendor details below before making a decision.</p>

            <!-- Vendor Preview Table -->
            <div class="preview-label">BATCH PREVIEW (TOP {{items.length}})</div>
            <table class="vendor-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Vendor & Banking Details</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Mode / Amount</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each items}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <div class="vendor-name">{{this.vendorName}} {{#if this.bpCode}}<span style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: normal;">({{this.bpCode}})</span>{{/if}}</div>
                            <div class="vendor-bank">
                                {{this.bankName}} • {{this.accountNumber}}<br/>
                                <span style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8;">IFSC: {{this.ifscCode}}</span>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                        <td class="amount-col">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;">{{this.transactionMode}}</div>
                            <div style="font-size: 15px;">{{../currency}} {{this.amount}}</div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            {{#if hasMoreItems}}
            <div class="more-indicator">
                + {{totalItems}} more items in this batch. View all details in the portal.
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="info-panel">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-key">Submitted By:</span>
                    <span class="info-val">{{submittedBy}} ({{submittedByEmail}})</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-key">Date Submitted:</span>
                    <span class="info-val">{{submittedAt}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-key">Project Link:</span>
                    <span class="info-val"><a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">View in Dashboard</a></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <div class="actions">
                <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="btn">Open Review Portal &rarr;</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Remote Approval Note -->
            <div class="remote-note">
                <h4>🏠 NOT IN THE OFFICE?</h4>
                <p>If you're away from your desk, you can simply <strong>reply</strong> to this email with <strong>"ACCEPT"</strong> or <strong>"REJECT"</strong> along with any comments. Our finance team will process it manually.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Kardex Finance Automation System</p>
            <p>This is a secure automated notification. Please do not share this link.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Kardex India. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>